high_descs: Move forward, turn right then head to the counter beside the microwave
Pick up the sponge beside the microwave
Turn right then face left to the sink
Put the sponge on the plate at the sink
Pick up the plate with sponge
Turn right walk forward then left face the last cabinet
Open the last cabinet put in the plate with sponge then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put in the plate with sponge in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn to the right and go back to the microwave.
Pick up the sponge on the left side of the counter.
Carry the sponge and take a step to the right to the sink.
Place the sponge on a plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate from the sink.
Carry the plate and turn around, then face right to the wall. Look up the the cabinet above the fridge.
Open the cabinet and place the plate inside, then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate and sponge to a cabinet.

high_descs: Go to the counter on the right of the microwave.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the sponge on the plate in the sink.
Pick up the plate with the sponge on it.
Go to the cabinet above the fridge on the right.
Put the plate and sponge in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a sponge on it in the cabinet.
